Text: Jamal Murray just won another shootout with Donovan Mitchell - JM 50 on 9-12 threes, DM 44 on 9-13 threes - then got emotional about his shoes with likenesses of George Floyd and Breonna Taylor and how much they motivate him. Well done, young man.
